### 3.2 Emotional Triggers

Core emotions that drive action:

| Emotion | Trigger Phrases |
|---------|----------------|
| **Fear** | "Don't miss out", "What if you're wrong?", "Protect yourself" |
| **Greed** | "Double your income", "Exclusive access", "Unfair advantage" |
| **Guilt** | "You deserve better", "Stop settling", "Owe it to yourself" |
| **Pride** | "Be the expert", "Impress your boss", "Stand out" |
| **Belonging** | "Join the movement", "You're one of us", "Be part of" |

