## 6. Sub-Agent Architecture

### Recommended Agent Types

| Agent | Purpose | Primary Frameworks |
|-------|---------|-------------------|
| **Headline Agent** | Generate/test headlines | 4U's, Three Rules, Awareness Stages |
| **Sales Copy Agent** | Long-form persuasion | AIDA, 4Ps, StoryBrand |
| **Ad Copy Agent** | Short-form conversion | PAS, BAB, Conflict Types |
| **Email Agent** | Sequences and campaigns | AIDA, PAS, Awareness Stages |
| **Positioning Agent** | Brand messaging strategy | Three Rules, Positioning Canvas, StoryBrand |
| **Review Agent** | Quality validation | Checklist, 4U's, Three Rules |
| **Awareness Agent** | Audience analysis | Schwartz 5 Stages, Cialdini Principles |

